# Global settings
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

# Account definition
IMAPAccount accounts
Host imap.strato.com
Port 993
User accounts@osphire.com
PassCmd "secret-tool lookup password accountsmail"
SSLType IMAPS

# Remote store
IMAPStore accounts-remote
Account accounts

# Local store
MaildirStore accounts-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/mail/accounts/
Inbox ~/mail/accounts/INBOX

# Channel (sync definition)
Channel accounts
Far :accounts-remote:
Near :accounts-local:
Patterns *



